  "keyFeatures": [
    "One-click server start/stop/restart with automatic EULA and crash detection",
    "Live dashboard with real-time CPU, RAM, TPS, uptime, and player count metrics",
    "Integrated dark-themed console with live log streaming and command input",
    "Automatic Playit.gg tunnel management for public multiplayer without port forwarding",
    "Player tracking via Minecraft log parsing — joins, leaves, chat, deaths, advancements, commands, kicks",
    "File manager with Monaco Editor for browsing and editing server files in-app",
    "Visual server.properties editor with ops, whitelist, and banned-players JSON management",
    "One-click ZIP backup creation and restore",
    "Multi-server management with per-server configuration",
    "Full Electron sandboxing with no Node.js access in the renderer process"
  ],
